cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.SE 

The paper discusses the development of a network-based security solution for mobile networks to detect anomalies and attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The solution also involves the use of analytical modelling, simulation, and learning, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of billing and control-plane data, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE).
